text: Jey Kugeler (18 April 1910 - 25 August 1983) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed at the 1936 Summer Olympics, the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1910 births Category:1983 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:People from Schifflange
